Version:          0.2.0
Release:          3%{?dist}%{?buildtag}
Summary:          Robust Tests for Differential Dispersion and DifferentialExpression in RNA-Sequencing Data

License:          GPL-3
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
